are sorted out. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=10776634\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>Kentucky has decided to stop telling people to boycott our state. They, along with West Virginia, called for the boycott after Sen. Lamar Alexander took action against mountain top removal. [<a href=\"http://www.nashvilleistalking.com/2009/07/kentucky-coal-calls-off-their-call-for-a-national-boycott-of-tennessee/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.nashvilleistalking.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Nashville Is Talking</a>]</li><li>A very lucky person won $200,000 from the Tennessee lottery in Clarksville. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/money/20155807/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>For those who have been following the whole affair-with-an-intern story about TN state senator Paul Stanley, the guy who is on trial for trying to extort Sen. Stanley is now claiming that a News Channel 5 reporter offered him $7,500 for some blackmail-y photos. [<a href=\"http://blogs.nashvillescene.com/pitw/2009/07/phil_williams_denies_hes_the_m.php\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;blogs.nashvillescene.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_self\">Pith In The Wind</a>]</li><li>One reporter also dug up a 1994 restraining order from Sen. Stanley&#x2019;s first wife alleging that he abused her physically and verbally. [<a href=\"http://politics.nashvillepost.com/2009/07/23/stanleys-first-wife-a-former-intern-swore-out-a-restraining-order-in-1994/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;politics.nashvillepost.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Post Politics</a>]</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/21506428@N03/3748060174/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">ryan2013</a>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/09/23/bright-early-thems-fightin-words-edition-2/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Them&#x2019;s Fightin&#x2019; Words Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Them&#x2019;s Fightin&#x2019; Words Edition</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/06/18/bright-early-thems-fightin-words-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Them&#x2019;s Fightin&#x2019; Words Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Them&#x2019;s Fightin&#x2019; Words Edition</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}